\id PRO  
\h Proverbs 
\toc1 Djambatj Yän 
\toc3 Proverbs 
\toc2 Proverbs 
\mt1 Djambatj Yän  
\c 3  
\p
\v 5 Nhunum ŋarru yaka mä-yuwalkmiyi Garraynham yuwalkkuman yana ŋay, mä-ṉiṉ’thuna nhanguḻ. Ga yaka mä-yuwalktjiya nhuŋguwaywurum marŋgiyinyarayu, ḻinygu djäwul nhunu djaŋu marŋgi bukmakkum nhäwu malaŋuwu.   